text: Andrei Ionuț Cerlincă (born 6 August 1995) is a Romanian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Liga III side Foresta Suceava.Foresta Suceava a testat câțiva tineri jucători într-un meci școală pe stadionul ”Areni”. svnews.ro ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Suceava Category:Romanian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Liga I players Category:Liga II players Category:ACS Foresta Suceava players Category:FC Rapid București players Category:SR Brașov players
title: Andrei Cerlincă
